    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一-列表的基本功能"><a href="#一-列表的基本功能" class="headerlink" title="一. 列表的基本功能"></a>一. 列表的基本功能</h1><h2 id="创建及初始化"><a href="#创建及初始化" class="headerlink" title="创建及初始化"></a>创建及初始化</h2><p>一维列表的创建及初始化较为简单，仅需要用中括号将数据括起来（数据与数据之间用逗号隔开）</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>]  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>n维列表的创建和初始化则要运用到循环，以二维列表举例建立一个3 * 3的列表</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">0</span>] * <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">3</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        x[i] = [<span class="number">0</span>] * <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[[<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>], [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>], [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意，下面这种构建二维列表的方式是错误的</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [[<span class="number">0</span>] * <span class="number">3</span>] * <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[[<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>], [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>], [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>两种方法在创建完成之后看起来是一模一样的，但是由于第二种方法等于嵌套时，列表的每一行指向  了相同的地址，导致改变某一行的某个元素时，其他行的对应元素也会改变，与嵌套列表定义不符。</p><h2 id="添加元素"><a href="#添加元素" class="headerlink" title="添加元素"></a>添加元素</h2><p>最一般的，可以利用列表对象所包含的方法append()在列表的最后添加一个元素，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.append(<span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>若希望同时添加多个元素，可使用extend()方法，在列表末尾添加若干个元素，注意，extend()相  当于用一个列表去扩充另一个列表，故使用时需要注意参数类型，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.extend([<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但在实际运用中，需求最多的是在某一个特定位置，添加一个元素，此时可以运用insert()方法实  现，insert()方法中含有两个参数，第一个为待插入的位置，第二个为待插入的元素值，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">5</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.insert(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="获取元素"><a href="#获取元素" class="headerlink" title="获取元素"></a>获取元素</h2><p>通过元素的索引值，可以直接获取列表中的某个元素，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x[<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>若要访问最后一个值，则可以使用反向索引进行访问，当索引值为负数时为反向索引，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x[-<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">4</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="删除元素"><a href="#删除元素" class="headerlink" title="删除元素"></a>删除元素</h2><p>删除元素，常用的有四种方式<br>remove()方法可以删除一个指定元素，前提是该元素必须在该列表中，若存在相同元素，则仅会删  除第一个，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.remove(<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>pop()方法则是弹出指定元素，及取出并且删除的意思，其参数是一个索引值，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.pop(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>] </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>clear()方法相对比较野蛮，但也很好理解，即直接清空列表，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.clear()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后一种方式则与前面三种不同，该方式所使用的不是列表所包含的方法，而是python语句–del。  该方式可以用于删除某个元素，也可以用于删除整个变量，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">del</span> x[<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">del</span> x</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">Traceback (most recent call last):</span><br><span class="line">  File <span class="string">&quot;&lt;pyshell#13&gt;&quot;</span>, line <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="keyword">in</span> &lt;module&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    x</span><br><span class="line">NameError: name <span class="string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> defined</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="二-列表切片"><a href="#二-列表切片" class="headerlink" title="二. 列表切片"></a>二. 列表切片</h1><h2 id="列表切片的基本用法"><a href="#列表切片的基本用法" class="headerlink" title="列表切片的基本用法"></a>列表切片的基本用法</h2><p>列表切片可以根据字面意思，简单的理解为在列表中切出我们所需要的片段，且对原列表无影响。  其基本格式为：<code>[开始位置索引值：结束位置索引值：步长] </code> (其中，步长省略时默认为1)<br>例如：  </p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x[<span class="number">0</span>:<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>特殊的，如果省略了开始位置则会获得从列表开头到结束位置的所有元素，同理，如果省略了结束位  置，则会获得从开始位置到列表末尾的所有元素，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x[:<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x[<span class="number">2</span>:]</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>] </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果同时省略了开始位置和结束位置，则可以获得一个原列表的复制，这也是列表浅拷贝的一种较为  简单的方式，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x[:]</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来在引入步长，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x[::<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果步长为负数，则相当于将列表翻转再根据步长的绝对值取值，以步长为-2举例：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x[::-<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">2</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="三-其他用法"><a href="#三-其他用法" class="headerlink" title="三. 其他用法"></a>三. 其他用法</h1><h2 id="列表推导式"><a href="#列表推导式" class="headerlink" title="列表推导式"></a>列表推导式</h2><p>列表推导式则是一个更加高级的用法，其逻辑上相当于一个嵌套循环，只是在形式上更加简单。<br>其基本结构为：<code>[表达式 for 变量 in 迭代对象 if 条件]</code>，举一个简单的例子：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [i <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">10</span>)]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">9</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不难想到，上述列表的构造也可以用循环实现：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">10</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        x.append(i)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">9</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这两种构造列表的方式虽然结果相同，但其原理却不相同。前者相当于创建了一个新列表并赋给变量  x；而后者则是利用循环和append()方法向已有的列表中增加元素。  </p><p>  除此之外，列表推导式基本结构中的for循环可以进行嵌套，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>z = [[x, y] <span class="keyword">for</span> x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">5</span>) <span class="keyword">if</span> x % <span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> y <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">5</span>) <span class="keyword">if</span> y % <span class="number">3</span> ==<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>z</span><br><span class="line">[[<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>], [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">3</span>], [<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0</span>], [<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>], [<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">0</span>], [<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>因此，列表推导式在确保功能的可实现性下，极大的缩短了代码的行数。</p><h2 id="常用操作符"><a href="#常用操作符" class="headerlink" title="常用操作符"></a>常用操作符</h2><p>比较操作符，如大于号小于号等，在列表中的比较原则与字符串的比较原则相同，列表中元素从第一  个开始比较，只要有一个大，即该列表大，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>y = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">3</span> ,<span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x &gt; y</span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">False</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>连接操作符(+)，允许将多个列表对象合并在一起，相当于extend()方法实现的功能，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>y = [<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x + y</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>虽然连接操作符与extend()方法的功能相同，但为了保证代码的规范和严谨，仍应使用extend()，  此外，连接操作符不能实现元素的添加。  </p><p>重复操作符(*)，即将一个字符串重复n次，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="string">&#x27;Love&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>y = x * <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>y</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">&#x27;Love&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Love&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Love&#x27;</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>需要注意的是，重复操作符所复制出的元素的地址值相同，故不能使用重复操作符进行嵌套列表的构  建。  </p><p>关系操作符(in/not in)，其功能为判断成员之间的关系，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="string">&#x27;I&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Love&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;You&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="string">&#x27;I&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> x</span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">True</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里需要注意一点，关系操作符仅能判断一个层次上的成员关系。</p><h2 id="列表包含的常用方法"><a href="#列表包含的常用方法" class="headerlink" title="列表包含的常用方法"></a>列表包含的常用方法</h2><p>count()方法用于统计元素在列表中出现的次数，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.count(<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>index()方法用于返回某元素在列表中第一次出现的索引值，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.index(<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>index()方法还可以三参数使用，其中第二和第三个参数分别为查找的起始点和终止点。  </p><p>reverse()方法用于翻转列表，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.reverse()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>sort()方法用于对列表元素进行从小到大的排序，例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x.sort()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">8</span>] </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
